data.description: An Unbeatable Opportunity!Looking for a move-in ready home that you can also renovate and watch the equity grow? Look no further! This spacious house has three bedrooms with cedar closets, two and a half bathrooms, and a generous basement with a full bath and ample storage space. The owner's suite, complete with attached bathroom, is located upstairs. With a little remodeling, you could transform this home into a three-bathroom haven! And that's not all - enjoy a large 20 x 40 in-ground pool, complete with a pool house that includes another full kitchen and half bath. 2 car garage and a long driveway leaving you plenty of space for parking. Don't let this amazing opportunity pass you by - make Munster, Indiana your new home today!
